text: Id estan wiwarawicquae ante subjecta eratto wii & to leanaham & et febresham:isealtern &iiwena gang mid cyninges wenum to blean ðem wiada.
&iiiioxnum gers mid cyninges oxnum, an wiwarawicxxx statera kasei et item x statera in aliawiwarawic &xxlamba &xxfehta.
Ab occidentecyninges folclandquod abet wighelm & wulflaf ab aquilonecuðrices dun heregeðelandab orientewighelmes landa meritiebiscepes land.
Hec sunt pratato wassingwellan stocmed healf be norðan hegforde be sturemeda sue ðer to limpað.
Ðis siondan ðes landes boec et Wassingwellan ðet Eðelbearht cyning Wullafe sealde his ðegne wið oðrum sue miclum lande et Mersaham.
Se cyning sealde & gebocade Wullafe fif sulung landes et Wassingwellan wið ðem fif sulungum et Mersaham.
& se cyning dyde ðet land et Mersaham him to folclande ða hie ðem landum iehwerfed hefdan butan ðem merscum & butan ðem sealtern et Fefresham & butan ðem wioda ðe to ðem sealtern limpð.
Ðis siondan ðes landes boc et Wassingwellan.
